Class Item

java.lang.Object
Item
public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
Provides methods and data types to create a Tool or Item for a shop. This class holds information about the item and knows who the item's supplier is.
Since:
2020-02-11
Version:
1.0
Author:
William Ledingham
